OL,3,CUK has 'tropical night' as record for
OL,4,Cwarmest May evening broken
OL,6,FThe UK has broken the record for the
OL,7,Fhottest night in May after
OL,8,Ftemperatures didn't fall below 21.3C
OL,9,Fin parts of the country.
OL,11,FThe temperature, recorded at Kenley
OL,12,FAirfield, south London, from Monday
OL,13,Finto Tuesday, means the evening can be
OL,14,Fclassified as a "tropical night", the
OL,15,FMet Office said.
OL,17,FTropical nights are above 20C, the
OL,18,Fnational weather service said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
