OL,3,CUK has 'tropical night' as record for
OL,4,Cwarmest May evening broken
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIt followed a record-breaking day,
OL,12,Fwith the UK recording its provisional
OL,13,Fall-time hottest meteorological spring
OL,14,Ftemperature when Kew Gardens in south-
OL,15,Fwest London hit 34.8C on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
