OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779891067
OL,3,CUK has 'tropical night' as record for
OL,4,Cwarmest May evening broken
OL,6,FThe Met Office listed 12 locations
OL,7,Fwhere the record was topped on Monday,
OL,8,Franging from Suffolk to Berkshire to
OL,9,FWarwickshire, while 97 of its
OL,10,Fmonitoring sites reached or surpassed
OL,11,F30C.
OL,13,FThe prior record for the warmest May
OL,14,Fnight was only set on Sunday, when
OL,15,Ftemperatures did not fall below 19.4C
OL,16,Fat Kenley Airfield.
OL,18,FBefore then, the previous May night
OL,19,Frecord was 18.9C, set in 1944, the Met
OL,20,FOffice said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
