OL,3,CUK has 'tropical night' as record for
OL,4,Cwarmest May evening broken
OL,6,F"Further heat is in the forecast for
OL,7,Fmuch of England and Wales, with
OL,8,Fsimilar temperatures forecast for
OL,9,FTuesday," said Dan Suri, chief
OL,10,Foperational meteorologist at the Met
OL,11,FOffice.
OL,13,F"High pressure is forecast to
OL,14,Fgradually lose its influence later in
OL,15,Fthe week, though maximum temperatures
OL,16,Fwill still remain high and in the low
OL,17,F30Cs for some mid-week and high 20Cs
OL,18,Flate this week."
